# Title: Azure Unusual Authentication Interruption
# Author: Austin Songer @austinsonger
# Date: 2021-11-26
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects when there is a interruption in the authentication process.
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.persistence, attack.initial-access, attack.stealth, attack.t1078
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/cloud/azure/signin_logs/azure_unusual_authentication_interruption.yml

(ResultDescription="Device authentication is required" ResultType=50097) OR (ResultDescription="DeviceAuthenticationFailed" ResultType=50155) OR (ResultDescription="ExternalSecurityChallenge - External security challenge was not satisfied" ResultType=50158)